                        medical education courses, Gladzor University has turned out to be a destination of students who
                        want to pursue MBBS in Armenia and more particularly among Indian students.
                    </p>
                    <p>The university is also characterized by high academic standards, modern infrastructure and
                        qualified faculty. Its MBBS program is taught in English and is therefore open to foreign
                        students, especially of India and other non-Armenian speaking nations.
                    </p>
